1. *Reka* je jako nabujala posle velikih kiša. (The *river* is very swollen after heavy rains.)
2. Videla sam *reku* dok sam šetala pored nje. (I saw the *river* while walking alongside it.)
3. *Rečica* koja protiče kroz selo je veoma pitoma. (The *little river* that flows through the village is very gentle.)
4. Naša kuća se nalazi nedaleko od *reke*. (Our house is located near the *river*.)
5. Turisti vole da pecaju ribu u ovoj *reci*. (Tourists love to fish in this *river*.)
6. Voda iz *reke* se koristi za navodnjavanje polja. (Water from the *river* is used for irrigation of fields.)
7. Nekada se *reke* koristile za prevoz robe. (Rivers were once used for transportation of goods.)
8. Čamac je sleteo u *reku* nakon što je ispao iz ruku. (The boat landed in the *river* after slipping from hands.)
9. U proleće *reke* se brzo pune snegom koji se topi. (In spring, *rivers* quickly fill up with snow that melts.)
10. Žabe žive u blizini *reke* gde imaju dovoljno vlage. (Frogs live near the *river* where they have enough moisture.)